information.author: Centreon

description.value:
**Plugin-Pack to monitor Azure Event Hubs service using RestAPI or AZCLI.**

*namespaces* & *clusters* are supported.
Available Host template and related Services:

|Cloud-Azure-Analytics-EventHubs-custom|
|---|
|Backlog|
|Connections|
|Errors|
|Health|
|Messages|
|Requests|
|Throughput|

This Plugin-Pack provides a Host discovery *provider* to be used with the Host discovery module.

**Plugin-Pack pour superviser les ressources Azure Event Hubs via RestAPI ou AZCLI.**

Ce Plugin-Pack est compatible avec les ressources de type *namespaces* & *clusters*.
Modèle d\'hôte disponibles et services associés:

|Cloud-Azure-Analytics-EventHubs-custom|
|---|
|Backlog|
|Connections|
|Errors|
|Health|
|Messages|
|Requests|
|Throughput|

Ce Plugin-Pack fournit un *provider* Host Discovery pour le module d\'auto-découverte d\'Hôtes
